<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038394" n="143v"/>
<p>
<lb/>Accepi die <date>11. hujus mensis</date> <rs key="B_1717-12-16_991170517037405501" type="letter">epistolam</rs> Tuam gratissimam die <date when="1717-12-09">9.</date> scriptam una
                    <lb/>cum quindecim libris, de quarum acceptione hac ipsa die certiorem facio
                    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruum</rs><note>Bernoulli, Johann (1667-1748)</note> meum, qui nisi consentiat, ut retineam hos nu<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>os, eosdem Tibi
                    <lb/>remittam. Gratias Tibi ago maximas, quod mihi responderis ad ea, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Te
                    <lb/>interrogaveram, quia scire cupis rationem cur eadem <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te petierim,
                    <lb/>eandem non celabo. Reddita nempe mihi fuerat <rs key="B_1717-12-16_991170517037405501" type="letter">epistola</rs> Tua <date>postridie
                    <lb/>ejus diei</date>, qua suam<del>eadem diem qu quam eadem die</del> acceperat <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Polenus</rs>, ad
                    <lb/>quem tamen eadem die qua ad me scripseras; jam si mea huic inclusa
                    <lb/>fuisset, non potuissem divinare, quid rationis subfuisset, cur <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Polenus</rs>
<lb/>integro die eam apud se retinuisset, antequam <subst><del><gap/></del><add>illam</add></subst> mihi redderet; quia
                    <lb/>autem, ut mihi significasti, meam seorsim misisti, oportet ut illa integro
                    <lb/>die diutius in Posta delituerit, quia forte <rs type="person">Magister Postarum</rs> <add>vel distributor epistolarum</add> tum tem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>poris locum me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> habitationis ignoravit. Quod me denuo invites in
                    <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>des Tuas post Lectiones meas absolutas, meamque pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentiam Tibi non
                    <lb/>solum gratam verum etiam utilem fore dicas, iterum su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>as ago gratias.
                    <lb/>Si rerum studiorumque meorum status permittet, Tibi morem geram;
                    <lb/>si non, poteris, si placet, exercitationem Tuam ad me mittere, egoque
                    <lb/>studiose exequar, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cumque <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me fieri voles, sum etenim ad man<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>data Tua paratissimus. En hic <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs><note type="internal">ToDo: Brief erfassen - Dieser Brief von Nicolaus I Bernoulli an Johann I Bernoulli ist anscheinend nicht erhalten.</note> ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruum</rs> meum, quam
                    <lb/>Te sic jubente ad Te mitto, ut crastina die Tuis, quas forte scribes, li<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>teris<note>Niclaus I Bernoullis Erwartung, dass Michelotti bald einen Brief an Johann I Bernoulli schickt, wird nicht erfüllt, der nächste Brief in dieser Korrespondenz datiert auf <rs key="B_1718-03-11_991170515152705501" type="letter">1718.03.11</rs></note> inclusam <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basileam</rs> transmittas.
                </p>
